# delivery-tracking session state (not committed)
.claude/tracking/

# Per-project Agile boards = LOCAL RUNTIME STATE, not source. Costs derive from each
# developer's own ~/.claude telemetry and the tracking hook re-saves the board after every
# commit, so committing it just churns/conflicts and leaks one machine's cost data. The
# dashboard regenerates it on demand; inspect structure via the dashboard / `cli list`, not git.
dashboard/data/boards/
